Q1. Write a python program to accept a string and substring from user. Check if a particular substring is present at the beginning of the given string, give appropriate message. (Use RE module) \

import re
s = input("Enter main string: ")
sub = input("Enter substring: ")
pattern = "^" + sub  
if re.match(pattern, s):
    print("Substring is present at the beginning.")
else:
    print("Substring is NOT present at the beginning.")


